Description:
    Install Scoof assets via manifests and some starter files

Example:
    rails generate scoof:install

    This will create:
        app/assets/javascripts/scoof.js
        app/assets/javascripts/scoof/init.js
        app/assets/stylesheets/mobile.scss
        app/assets/stylesheets/tablet.scss
        app/assets/stylesheets/desktop.scss
        app/templates/layout/_head.html.mustache
        app/templates/layout/_body.html.mustache
